'''James Anderson''' is a member of the [http://www.myuselessknowledge.com/swfa Star Wars Fanboy Association] who wrote a series of short comics titled ''[[Bungo n' Rusti]]''. The first story, ''[[Bungo n' Rusti Get Carry-Out]]'', was published in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 11|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 11]]. Others were originally slated to appear in the Adventure Journal, but, as [[Dark Horse Comics]] held the sole ''[[Star Wars]]'' comics license, the plans were scrapped. Several more unofficial stories were published online at [[TheForce.net]].

